{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"All human life,"},{"time":2000,"text":"all life, depends on plants."},{"time":5000,"text":"Let me try to convince you of that in a few seconds."},{"time":9000,"text":"Just think for a moment."},{"time":11000,"text":"It doesn't matter whether you live in a small African village,"},{"time":14000,"text":"or you live in a big city,"},{"time":16000,"text":"everything comes back to plants in the end:"},{"time":18000,"text":"whether it's for the food, the medicine,"},{"time":20000,"text":"the fuel, the construction, the clothing, all the obvious things;"},{"time":23000,"text":"or whether it's for the spiritual and recreational things"},{"time":26000,"text":"that matter to us so much;"},{"time":28000,"text":"or whether it's soil formation,"},{"time":30000,"text":"or the effect on the atmosphere,"},{"time":32000,"text":"or primary production."},{"time":34000,"text":"Damn it, even the books here are made out of plants."},{"time":37000,"text":"All these things, they come back to plants."},{"time":40000,"text":"And without them we wouldn't be here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":43000,"text":"Now plants are under threat."},{"time":45000,"text":"They're under threat because of changing climate."},{"time":47000,"text":"And they are also under threat because they are sharing a planet"},{"time":49000,"text":"with people like us."},{"time":51000,"text":"And people like us want to do things that destroy plants,"},{"time":54000,"text":"and their habitats."},{"time":56000,"text":"And whether that's because of food production,"},{"time":58000,"text":"or because of the introduction of alien plants"},{"time":61000,"text":"into places that they really oughtn't be,"},{"time":64000,"text":"or because of habitats being used for other purposes --"},{"time":67000,"text":"all these things are meaning that plants have to adapt,"},{"time":71000,"text":"or die, or move."},{"time":74000,"text":"And plants sometimes find it rather difficult to move"},{"time":76000,"text":"because there might be cities and other things in the way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79000,"text":"So if all human life depends on plants,"},{"time":82000,"text":"doesn't it make sense that perhaps we should try to save them?"},{"time":84000,"text":"I think it does."},{"time":86000,"text":"And I want to tell you about a project to save plants."},{"time":89000,"text":"And the way that you save plants"},{"time":91000,"text":"is by storing seeds."},{"time":93000,"text":"Because seeds, in all their diverse glory,"},{"time":97000,"text":"are plants' futures."},{"time":99000,"text":"All the genetic information for future generations of plants"},{"time":102000,"text":"are held in seeds."},{"time":104000,"text":"So here is the building;"},{"time":106000,"text":"it looks rather unassuming, really."},{"time":109000,"text":"But it goes down below ground many stories."},{"time":111000,"text":"And it's the largest seed bank in the world."},{"time":113000,"text":"It exists not only in southern England,"},{"time":116000,"text":"but distributed around the world. I'll come to that."},{"time":119000,"text":"This is a nuclear-proof facility."},{"time":121000,"text":"God forbid that it should have to withstand that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":124000,"text":"So if you're going to build a seed bank, you have to decide"},{"time":126000,"text":"what you're going to store in it. Right?"},{"time":128000,"text":"And we decided that what we want to store first of all,"},{"time":130000,"text":"are the species that are most under threat."},{"time":133000,"text":"And those are the dry land species."},{"time":135000,"text":"So first of all we did deals"},{"time":138000,"text":"with 50 different countries."},{"time":140000,"text":"It means negotiating with heads of state,"},{"time":143000,"text":"and with secretaries of state in 50 countries"},{"time":145000,"text":"to sign treaties."},{"time":147000,"text":"We have 120 partner institutions all over the world,"},{"time":149000,"text":"in all those countries colored orange."},{"time":152000,"text":"People come from all over the world to learn,"},{"time":154000,"text":"and then they go away and plan exactly how"},{"time":156000,"text":"they're going to collect these seeds."},{"time":159000,"text":"They have thousands of people all over the world"},{"time":161000,"text":"tagging places where those plants are said to exist."},{"time":164000,"text":"They search for them. They find them in flower."},{"time":166000,"text":"And they go back when their seeds have arrived."},{"time":170000,"text":"And they collect the seeds. All over the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":173000,"text":"The seeds -- some of if is very untechnical."},{"time":177000,"text":"You kind of shovel them all in to bags and dry them off."},{"time":180000,"text":"You label them. You do some high-tech things here and there,"},{"time":183000,"text":"some low-tech things here and there."},{"time":186000,"text":"And the main thing is that you have to dry them"},{"time":188000,"text":"very carefully, at low temperature."},{"time":191000,"text":"And then you have to store them"},{"time":193000,"text":"at about minus 20 degrees C --"},{"time":195000,"text":"that's about minus four Fahrenheit, I think --"},{"time":197000,"text":"with a very critically low moisture content."},{"time":201000,"text":"And these seeds will be able to germinate,"},{"time":204000,"text":"we believe, with many of the species,"},{"time":207000,"text":"in thousands of years,"},{"time":209000,"text":"and certainly in hundreds of years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":212000,"text":"It's no good storing the seeds if you don't know they're still viable."},{"time":215000,"text":"So every 10 years we do germination tests"},{"time":218000,"text":"on every sample of seeds that we have."},{"time":221000,"text":"And this is a distributed network."},{"time":223000,"text":"So all around the world people are doing the same thing."},{"time":226000,"text":"And that enables us to develop germination protocols."},{"time":229000,"text":"That means that we know the right combination of heat"},{"time":232000,"text":"and cold and the cycles that you have to get"},{"time":234000,"text":"to make the seed germinate."},{"time":237000,"text":"And that is very useful information."},{"time":239000,"text":"And then we grow these things,"},{"time":241000,"text":"and we tell people, back in the countries where these seeds have come from,"},{"time":245000,"text":"\"Look, actually we're not just storing this"},{"time":247000,"text":"to get the seeds later,"},{"time":249000,"text":"but we can give you this information about"},{"time":251000,"text":"how to germinate these difficult plants.\""},{"time":253000,"text":"And that's already happening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255000,"text":"So where have we got to?"},{"time":257000,"text":"I am pleased to unveil that our three billionth seed --"},{"time":260000,"text":"that's three thousand millionth seed --"},{"time":263000,"text":"is now stored."},{"time":265000,"text":"Ten percent of all plant species on the planet,"},{"time":268000,"text":"24,000 species are safe;"},{"time":271000,"text":"30,000 species, if we get the funding, by next year."},{"time":274000,"text":"Twenty-five percent of all the world's plants, by 2020."},{"time":278000,"text":"These are not just crop plants,"},{"time":280000,"text":"as you might have seen stored in Svalbard in Norway --"},{"time":283000,"text":"fantastic work there."},{"time":285000,"text":"This is at least 100 times bigger."},{"time":288000,"text":"We have thousands of collections that have been sent out"},{"time":291000,"text":"all over the world:"},{"time":293000,"text":"drought-tolerant forest species sent to Pakistan and Egypt;"},{"time":296000,"text":"especially photosynthetic-efficient plants"},{"time":300000,"text":"come here to the United States;"},{"time":303000,"text":"salt-tolerant pasture species sent to Australia;"},{"time":306000,"text":"the list goes on and on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":308000,"text":"These seeds are used for restoration."},{"time":310000,"text":"So in habitats that have already been damaged,"},{"time":313000,"text":"like the tall grass prairie here in the USA,"},{"time":316000,"text":"or in mined land in various countries,"},{"time":318000,"text":"restoration is already happening because of these species --"},{"time":322000,"text":"and because of this collection."},{"time":324000,"text":"Some of these plants, like the ones on the bottom"},{"time":326000,"text":"to the left of your screen,"},{"time":328000,"text":"they are down to the last few remaining members."},{"time":331000,"text":"The one where the guy is collecting seeds there on the truck,"},{"time":335000,"text":"that is down to about 30 last remaining trees."},{"time":337000,"text":"Fantastically useful plant,"},{"time":339000,"text":"both for protein and for medicine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":342000,"text":"We have training going on in China, in the USA,"},{"time":346000,"text":"and many other countries."},{"time":349000,"text":"How much does it cost?"},{"time":351000,"text":"2,800 dollars per species is the average."},{"time":355000,"text":"I think that's cheap, at the price."},{"time":357000,"text":"And that gets you all the scientific data"},{"time":359000,"text":"that goes with it."},{"time":361000,"text":"The future research is \"How can we find"},{"time":364000,"text":"the genetic and molecular markers"},{"time":366000,"text":"for the viability of seeds,"},{"time":368000,"text":"without having to plant them every 10 years?\""},{"time":370000,"text":"And we're almost there."},{"time":372000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":374000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}